<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>GRACIOUS SPIRIT, HOLY GHOST</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw Lalpa ka chung u-ah,
 Penticost ni tun sakin;
 Na van vangpiek ka ngai ui,
 Ei suhalh dingin.

[V2]
 2. Thil lopi cheng bei ina,
 Himahleh nei hehpihna;
 Mang puona, kumsawt inle,
 Um zing zing ina.

[V3]
 3. Nang dinga kimang dingin,
 Aw Lalpa, ei panpih in;
 Na nasep ding nei piek hi,
 Kipakin sem ka.

[V4]
 4. Thempa'n ei them mahlele,
 Hang takin ding hitiu ie;
 Lalpa sulnung zui zelin,
 Pang tei tei hitiu.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>212</hymn_number>
</song>